These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, polish, japanese, mexican
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, tiparillo, bluemaster, fonseca
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, fish, lizard, cat
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, juice, 7up, iced-tea
 1. the owner of the fish is not to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##8
 2. the person drinking tea is not to the left of the person drinking tea##8
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the left of the owner of the cat##8
 5. the person drinking tea is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
 6. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 7. the polish is somewhere to the right of the american##5
 8. the fonseca-smoker is between the person drinking juice and the owner of the fish##2
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is the bluemaster-smoker##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the mexican##1
11. the japanese is on the left or right of the davidoff-smoker##3
12. the mexican is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
13. the bluemaster-smoker is not to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##8
14. the polish is the person drinking 7up##1
15. the polish is not the owner of the fish##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Nationality         | american     | polish   | mexican | japanese |
| Cigar   | tiparillo | fonseca   | davidoff   | bluemaster  |
| Pet         | fish  | lizard  | cat  | hedgehog |
| Beverage     | tea    | 7up | juice     | iced-tea    |

