The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, soccer, biathlon, tennis
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, sunflower, iris, tulip
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, designer, architect, photographer
 1. the person who growsiris is between the police-officer and the person who growssunflower##2
 2. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the right of the designer##8
 3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
 4. the person playing bridge is not to the right of the photographer##8
 5. the police-officer is not to the left of the person who growssunflower##8
 6. the person who's sport is tennis is not to the right of the person playing domino##8
 7. the architect is somewhere to the left of the photographer##5
 8. the architect is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who growsorchid is the designer##1
10. the person who growsiris is on the left or right of the police-officer##3
11. the police-officer is not to the left of the person who growsiris##8
12. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
13. the person who growstulip is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##5
14. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person who growsiris##3
15. the person playing bridge is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
17. the person playing bridge is not to the right of the person who growssunflower##8
18. the person who's sport is soccer is not to the right of the designer##8
19. the person playing domino is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
