4 different pets are kept: rat, chinchilla, goldfish, rabbit
 1. the person traveling to rome is not the person who's birthday is in october##6
 2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
 3. the person driving the ship is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 4. the person driving the van is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's birthday is in december##2
 5. the person traveling to rome is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
 6. the owner of the rat is not to the right of the person driving the van##8
 7. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an odd position##4
 8. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to boston##5
 9. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
10. the person who's birthday is in december is the owner of the rat##1
11. the owner of the chinchilla is not to the right of the person driving the motorbike##8
12. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
13. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
14. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
15. the person traveling to boston is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
