4 different games are played: bridge, domino, snooker, backgammon
 1. the person playing bridge is the person playing bridge##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##5
 3. the person playing domino is somewhere to the left of the person playing snooker##5
 4. the person playing domino is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 5. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left##1
 8. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 9. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##5
10. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
11. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
13. the person playing backgammon is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##8
14. the person who's birthday is in november is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##8
